l/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果pogba 同rojo要停賽,賽後足總有片都可以追加啦,依家係足總唔追究, 你可以話佢黑,但黑還黑,錄影判決還錄影判決</blockquote><br />\n即係話有錄影睇都可以黑囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daeee570b7d5b8fd9c19a8d4e14ab127f144814b","tid":187381,"uid":23649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:49:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果有錄影判決你連第五都未必有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有錄影判決<br />\nPogba、ibra打mma 俾人停左賽3場<br />\nRojo連續2場雙腳飛鏟又停左賽十世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果pogba 同rojo要停賽,賽後足總有片都可以追加啦,依家係足總唔追究, 你可以話佢黑,但黑還黑,錄影判決還錄影判決</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2樣野<br />\nRojo個2樣足總唔秋後算帳<br />\n係因為球證睇唔到雙腳落同就住個犯規俾左黃牌<br />\n第時有錄影判決rojo個2野<br />\n球證可即時補番俾紅牌"},{"pid":"0d5093df84183948bbeeb0a3a2d18c8ceb11bdfa","tid":187381,"uid":34513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:50:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要買VAR！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8bbe59290d8930fd723c24f10ffdfcc486324e8b","tid":187381,"uid":45335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:12:35.000Z","msg":"有既話你有冇聯賽杯都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79ec1ee2811adb1def66e23375a870964800813","tid":187381,"uid":23649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:23:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有既話你有冇聯賽杯都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢句真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9516975cc2ccfc5506af8ff265303e27870f1d07","tid":187381,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:24:22.000Z","msg":"有賽後追罰但普巴都唔洗停啦<br />\n錄影判決=獌鏡"}]}